videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan doesn't get the foul call, leading to Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu knocking down the 3-pointer on the other end.
videos.headline: Dosunmu hits the 3 after the no-foul call

videos.description: Aaron Jordan finds the cutting Tevian Jones for the one-handed dunk to bring Illinois within two.
videos.headline: Illinois' Jones flushes backdoor dunk

videos.description: Maryland's Bruno Fernando throws down the monster two-handed jam on the inbounds play.
videos.headline: Fernando dunks it with authority
